data.description: Absolute beauty in the sought-after Dove Creek Subdivision! The 5 bedrooms and 2 living rooms provide ample space and room to grow. A fully finished, modern basement includes a dry bar (that just needs a sink *already plumbed* to become a wet bar), secure storage room, and a hidden bookcase door! Two master bedrooms provide options to live on either level or room for guests. Outside you'll enjoy the trex deck with retractable awning, and manicured yard. Grab a handful of raspberries or blackberries off the bushes and enjoy the beauty! Plenty of space to park your boat or RV! Square footage per previous appraisal. Buyer to verify all information.
